e27::a "10.1. The Consultant will defend and indemnify the Company, its affiliates, representatives from and against any claim or action commenced by a third party alleging that the Services or Deliverables provided infringes copyrights, trademark, patent or other intellectual property and will indemnify Company, its affiliates, representatives from any costs, [including reasonable attorneys' fees], which result from the defense or settlement of and/or damages finally awarded against the Company, its affiliates, representatives in any such claim." ::e
